- Using Make: ---------------------------------------------------

 To install:

  $ make
  $ make install

  Edit /etc/slapt-getrc (see README for details)

 To uninstall:

  $ make uninstall

- Using pkgtools: -----------------------------------------------

 To install:

  $ make slackpkg
  $ installpkg ./slackpkg/slapt-get-0.9.tgz

 To uninstall:

  $ removepkg slapt-get-0.9
